'''Aɣyul''', d yiwwen uɣeṛsiw asuṭṭaḍ seg twacult n yiɣeṛsiwen igmariyen (équidés), mecṭuḥ seddaw n uɛawdiw, imeẓẓuɣen-is d imeqṛanen. Aɣyul yettwasnen aṭas gar wiyyaḍ d aɣyul aqeddac (âne domestique) i d-yekkan seg usegred n waɣyul azagir n Tefriqt (âne sauvage d'Afrique), seg-s frurin-d aṭas n yiriten.

==Amawal==

Awtem : Aɣyul.

Tawtemt : Taɣyult.

Asgʷet amalay : Iɣyal.

Asgʷet unti : Tiɣyal 

Aɣyul amecṭuḥ isem-is : Ajḥiḥ.

==Ccetlat yettwasnen n yiɣyal==
Aṭas n tulmisin tisnalaɣanin (caractéristiques morphologiques) am uqaṛṛu, tamgeṛt akkʷed iḍaṛṛen s yis-nt nezmer ad nẓeṛ ccetlat yellan<ref name="Farissier14">{{harvsp|Farissier|2007|p=14-15}}</ref> :<br>
* Aɣyul amagnu : d aɣyul aqeddac i d-yekkan seg uɣyul azagir n Tefriqt, ass-a yettidir deg yimenẓawen akk;
* Aɣyul azagir n Tefriqt, yettidir deg usamar, ladɣa deg Ṣumal;
* Aɣyul azagir n Asya, yettidir deg Asya talemmast, ccetla-agi deg-s i d-yedda uɣyul n yihendiyen;
* Aɣyul azagir n Tibet neɣ Kiang, yettidir deg yidurar n Himalaya;
* Aɣyul n Turuft, yettidir deg tmura n Turuft n unẓul, yettidir daɣen deg tmura n Usamar-Alemmas.<br>
Iɣyal izagiren ass-agi ttwagzen s ngar, kra deg-sen ttwasigzen deg wumuɣ azeggʷaɣ n Tddukli Tagraɣlant n Useḥbiber ɣef Ugama (UICN : Union internationale pour la conservation de la nature).<br>

